entry.title: ltuckr/flavor-impersonator
entry.summary: A copycat recipe app that combines the use of Node.js, Express.js, Handlebars.js, MySQL, and Sequelize. It allows users to discover and share their favorite restaurant or famous dish recipes, replicating them at home.
